{
  "stem": "14168.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, while I went to school, the last few years, I coached students, younger students, those who were just one grade below me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I helped them with their Latin, I helped them with their French and whatever else they had, except mathematics.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There I would have needed some coaching myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that way I paid for my vacation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I also was very good at-- at painting-- signs, for instance, for my mother's store, all of this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- well, those were the useful hobbies that I had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for instance, 'Entrance here' or 'Exit there,' whatever the case may be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that, that, of course, became known.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I was called upon to do a few things for friends, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't spend any time there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just picked up my mother once in awhile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't, but-- and I went to my father's store.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was, as I mentioned, a sales representative.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he sometimes had need for a foreign correspondent in French.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He dealt with Belgium, and so I helped him with my, with my French, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was up until 1933.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then things started changing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember the first act against the Jews that the Nazis took, other than throwing them-- throwing them out, actually, of courts and prohibiting them from practicing law and throwing them out as civil servants and also depriving them of the privilege of practicing medicine.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They instituted, or called for, a boycott day-- boycott of the Jews on the 1st of April, 1933.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were Nazis-- and I still remember them, standing in front of my mother's store, of every Jewish store-- don't buy from Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some of my friends' fathers or mothers committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Jewish friend.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
